{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_vrtx_01XokGEk9jZnAoQD1PEj3c3V","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the architecture. The CPPC's `NamespaceSelector` is applied at the webhook configuration level (`internal/controller/operator/podplacement_objects.go:42`), not within the webhook handler's Go code. The webhook handler's `shouldIgnorePod` has its own hardcoded exclusions (`kube-*` prefix, operator namespace, etc.).\n\nSo the CPPC `NamespaceSelector` controls which namespaces the MutatingWebhookConfiguration intercepts, but the webhook handler itself additionally filters based on `shouldIgnorePod` logic.\n\nNow, the key question: why would a pod in `openshift-kube-apiserver` NOT get the scheduling gate?\nLooking at the exclusion logic, `openshift-kube-apiserver` doesn't match the `kube-*` prefix check, so that's not filtering it out. The other conditions depend on whether the pod has already been scheduled, if it has control plane node selectors, or if it's from a DaemonSet—kube-apiserver pods are typically static pods rather than DaemonSet-managed, so those checks might not be excluding them either.\n\nThe test scenario seems to be checking that even when the ClusterPodPlacementConfig has a namespaceSelector matching all namespaces, the kube-apiserver pod still shouldn't be gated. Looking at the existing test setup, the CPPC is already created without a specific NamespaceSelector, which means it applies to all namespaces by default. The pod creation call gets intercepted by the webhook, and the test just verifies it succeeds without errors, but doesn't actually validate whether the scheduling gate was applied or not. I should check how other tests in the package verify scheduling gates to understand the proper assertion pattern.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1244,"cache_read_input_tokens":65163,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1244,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"012c9df5-6571-43ba-8518-84ca4932300f","uuid":"6cf48681-a9ca-4d73-90ae-e6290c03c6ce","timestamp":"2026-07-20T17:48:29.799Z","request_id":"req_vrtx_011CdDjHd7xJ8GmUKNiMFva7"}
